2026-05-15T06:23:35.4971071Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4971914Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4972669Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4973424Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4974364Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4975259Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T06:23:35.4976109Z 257            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
